short_description: This US-SJ-60/FM1000 model equipment is used for the production of polyethylene bags and serves for the production of products from 50 kg to 120 kg per hour. The total power of the equipment is 66 kW, the thickness of the film is 0.008-0.10 mm, and the total weight is 4000 kg. Other models of this equipment are also shown in the description, and their prices differ depending on the model.

Uskunaning umumiy quvvati 66 kW, plyonkaning qalinligi 0.008-0.10 mm va umumiy vazni 4000 kg ni tashkil qiladi. Tavsifda shu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ularning narxlari modellariga qarab farqlanadi.
